  Source:
    Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Beauty-Peace=Peace=Serenity
---
When a man has restrained the turbulent passions of his breast by the power of
right judgment, and has spread the garment of soft compassion and sweet
content over his heart and mind, let him then worship divine serenity within
himself.
